{"tid":889501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東涌迫爆　居民投訴噪音及垃圾滿地","createTime":"2018-11-04T15:16:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-07T02:01:20.000Z","uid":79563,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b25d1147756b156ba3af03a80e9446220b3d2d20","tid":889501,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T15:16:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181104/s00001/b89112b3a408d6cee1a78de1f3b051f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181104%2Fs00001%2Fb89112b3a408d6cee1a78de1f3b051f4.jpg&h=18e2a43e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181104/s00001/b540c7a5af64b036f20dfad2b1155604.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181104%2Fs00001%2Fb540c7a5af64b036f20dfad2b1155604.jpg&h=4fc00067&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港珠澳大橋開通後第二個周六及周日，東涌人山人海，民建聯區議員周浩鼎指，不少內地旅行團帶旅客經港珠海澳大橋來港，然後安排團友坐巴士到最近大橋的東涌，結果迫爆東涌，指今日情況比周六更差，連日不少居民向他投訴，東涌港鐵站外的廣場下午擠滿旅客等巴士到大橋口岸，造成噪音滋擾，又有居民投訴旅客在廣場進食，遺下垃圾，造成衛生及觀瞻問題，而大量旅客湧到東涌，食店及便利店都迫爆，影響居民生活。<br />\n<br />\n周浩鼎指，這兩天一直在東涌觀察情況，並致電官員及巴士公司等處理事件，要求短期內先把接駁大橋的巴士站，由東涌東薈城搬到較遠民居的昂坪360纜車車站外，冀避免人潮聚集屋苑附近，指運房局回覆稱會考慮有關建議。<br />\n<br />\n周浩鼎又指，現時大橋的直通巴士只開通一半運力，不少內地團於是安排旅行團坐「金巴」到香港口岸，然後選擇附近的東涌作為行程點，結果大量旅客擠在東涌。他聯繫旅遊業界及官員，要求跟內地旅行社商討，不要把東涌作為內地團旅遊終站，又要求政府盡快與業界商討，開通更多直通巴士，由大橋往各區，分流旅客。他批評政府在大橋的交通配套安排不足，令到東涌居民不便。<br />\n<br />\n周浩鼎指，這兩天所見，旅行團客於下午4時至7時聚集，等候巴士赴大橋口岸，指今日警方已加派人手到場協助維持秩序，而巴士公司有加派巴士接載，但上客效率仍有待改善。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181104/s00001/b4e453bdb5f2f3e1397ed12b049478bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181104%2Fs00001%2Fb4e453bdb5f2f3e1397ed12b049478bd.jpg&h=666660bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181104/s00001/b544c9d7ed927f2dfd87b0fd63a01f35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181104%2Fs00001%2Fb544c9d7ed927f2dfd87b0fd63a01f35.jpg&h=00951604&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181104/s00001/b548ff41b96bda7beaaf290cd0c4017b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181104%2Fs00001%2Fb548ff41b96bda7beaaf290cd0c4017b.jpg&h=84510fbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181104/s00001/b54ebec3d9129131d4a98b681e394d3f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181104%2Fs00001%2Fb54ebec3d9129131d4a98b681e394d3f.jpg&h=5d0d2d68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181104/s00001/b55065e0e393ff8905028838ea20ef2f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181104%2Fs00001%2Fb55065e0e393ff8905028838ea20ef2f.jpg&h=b968b19a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181104/s00001/b5526bc5c580d4d699fbcdd1f0606460.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181104%2Fs00001%2Fb5526bc5c580d4d699fbcdd1f0606460.jpg&h=5d8cd4e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181104/s00001/b559aa09f344229c7d622e37f29243f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181104%2Fs00001%2Fb559aa09f344229c7d622e37f29243f6.jpg&h=3c0ca416&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181104/s00001/b5fec7beecf1ec9cbbe24b5349656b18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181104%2Fs00001%2Fb5fec7beecf1ec9cbbe24b5349656b18.jpg&h=822b60bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181104/s00001/b6009ff2f503803533a9227af9a1dd52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181104%2Fs00001%2Fb6009ff2f503803533a9227af9a1dd52.jpg&h=0daca273&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"26b20390c2c26985ebedeb655eec1a1c83d60d81","tid":889501,"uid":55533,"